Nodes.Comment: You can [weapon-swap] destroy the Nests. Just clear both tunnels under the walkways and you'll be done.
Do the Event if it's up. If not, move on.
Now Lure Drakes. You can Lure 2 at a time.
If the Event was not up before, the Heart is probably not done. Go West and finish.
You could kill Ogres along the road but the Houses in the camp up ahead give a lot of progress.
Do the Event if it's up.
You can [weapon-swap] interact with the Traps/Weapons/Shiny-things.
You can [weapon-swap] repair the Pet Houses. Go to the end of the cave and Train the Raptor pets (just spam the dialog options), repair the Pet Houses, pick up Chickens and put them in Cages.
The Stealthed spotters vanish from time to time, this is when you can pass. When on higher ground (roofs, etc) remember to Glide, it saves time.
